name: Shantu (XXIII Collection)
description:
She has a saintly aura, a classy essence, she walks with power, and is considered a role model and hero to many, she is famously known as a world-wide professional model, stunning both in photos and in reality, the best experience yet is to pay a hefty price to sit in a top designer’s fashion show and await this queen to catwalk by. Shantu owns her own shampoo and essential oils line called -you guessed it- Shantu. 
You can own this idol concept today and proudly keep her in your collection, she brings luck and fortune.
